---
const offerings = [
  'One number for safe spending',
  'Priorities first, not last',
  'Reserves for lean seasons',
  'Peace instead of anxiety',
];
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-36 bg-warm-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">

      <!-- Left column: Content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <p class="text-storehouse-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase reveal">
          Today
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-text-deep leading-[1.05] reveal reveal-delay-1">
          We need margin<br />
          more than ever.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg text-text-body leading-relaxed max-w-xl reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <p>
            The world encourages optimization: max out your mortgage, lifestyle
            up with every raise, fill every dollar with purpose.
          </p>
          <p>
            The result? A generation drowning in financial anxiety.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Italic closer -->
        <p class="mt-12 font-quote text-xl sm:text-2xl text-text-deep italic leading-snug max-w-lg reveal reveal-delay-3">
          Bob probably doesn't know the impact he had.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column: What Storehouse offers -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="bg-warm-cream rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-storehouse-100/60">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-text-deep mb-6">
            Storehouse offers a different path:
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-5">
            {offerings.map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-storehouse-500"></span>
                <span class="text-lg text-text-body">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
